-- https://steamcommunity.com/id/uliadev/ bother me if the script breaks
function onLoad()
    setNotes("\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nHarmonies: Re-Scripted [ulia]")
    allObjects = getAllObjects()
    local tokenBoard = nil
    setupButton = nil
    refillButton = nil
    scoreCubeBag = nil
    cardSlots = {}
    for i, o in ipairs(allObjects) do
        --if o.hasTag("Card") then
        --    local initialPosition = o.getPosition()
        --    local raisePosition = Vector(initialPosition.x, 2.1, initialPosition.z)
        --    o.setPosition(raisePosition)
        --end
        if o.hasTag("cardSlot") then
            o.setColorTint({0,0,0,0.4})
            table.insert(cardSlots, o)
        end
        if o.hasTag("Locked") then
            o.setLock(true)
            o.interactable = false
        end
        if o.hasTag("Spirit") then
            local snapParameters = {
                {
                    position=Vector(-0.82,0.2,-1.35),
                    rotation=Vector(0,0,0),
                    rotation_snap = true,
                    tags={}
                }
            }
            o.setSnapPoints(snapParameters)
            o.setLock(true)
        end
        if o.hasTag("Animal") then
            o.setLock(true)
        end
        if o.hasTag("Tokenboard") then
            tokenBoard = o
        end
        if o.hasTag("Setupbutton") then
            setupButton = o
        end
        if o.hasTag("Refillbutton") then refillButton = o end
        if o.hasTag("scoreCubeBag") then scoreCubeBag = o end
    end
    local tokenBoardRotationOffset = Vector(tokenBoard.getRotation().x, tokenBoard.getRotation().y - 38, tokenBoard.getRotation().z)
    tokenBoard.setRotation(Vector(0, -37, 0))
    spirits = false
    spiritIndex = 0
    animalIndex = 0
    animalPositions = {
        Vector(26.40, 2.1, 9.50),
        Vector(26.40, 2.1, 5.70),
        Vector(26.40, 2.1, 1.90),
        Vector(26.40, 2.1, -1.90),
        Vector(26.40, 2.1, -5.70)
    }
    animalDeckPosition = Vector(26.40, 2, -9.50)
    tokenIndex = 0
    --gameSetup()
    setupUI()
end

function setupUI()
    refillButton.setScale({0,0,0})
    refillButton.setColorTint({1,1,1,0})
    setupButton.setColorTint({1,1,1,0})
    setupButton.setPosition({13.5, 3, 0})
    local setupParams = {
        click_function = "gameSetup",
        function_owner = Global,
        label          = "START GAME",
        position       = {0, -0.5, 0},
        rotation       = {0, 180, 0},
        width          = 2000,
        height         = 500,
        font_size      = 300,
        color          = {1, 1, 1},
        font_color     = {0.2, 0.2, 0.2},
        scale          = {0.5, 0.5, 0.5}
    }
    setupButton.createButton(setupParams)
    local refillParams = {
        click_function = "refillComponents",
        function_owner = Global,
        label          = "REFILL STUFF",
        position       = {0, -0.5, 0},
        rotation       = {0, 180, 0},
        width          = 2000,
        height         = 500,
        font_size      = 300,
        color          = {1, 1, 1},
        font_color     = {0.2, 0.2, 0.2},
        scale          = {0.5, 0.5, 0.5}
    }
    refillButton.createButton(refillParams)
    local refillCubesParameters = {
        click_function = "refillCubes",
        function_owner = Global,
        label          = "",
        position       = {0.4, 0.5, -0.6},
        rotation       = {0, 180, 0},
        width          = 1700,
        height         = 1000,
        font_size      = 500,
        color          = {0.843, 0.313, 0.054},
        font_color     = {0.2, 0.2, 0.2},
        scale          = {0.05, 0.05, 0.05},
        tooltip        = "Refill Score Cubes"
    }
    for c, cardSlot in ipairs(cardSlots) do
        cardSlot.createButton(refillCubesParameters)
    end
end

function refillComponents()
    refillAnimals()
    setupTokens()
end

function gameSetup()
    setupButton.setScale({0,0,0})
    setupButton.setPosition({9000,9000,9000})
    refillButton.setScale({5,1,5})
    refillButton.setPosition({13.5, 3, 0})
    pickPlayer()
    Wait.time(function() setupSpirits() end, 0.5, 1)
    Wait.time(function() setupAnimals() end, 1, 1)
    Wait.time(function() setupTokens() end, 1.25, 1)
end

function pickPlayer()
    Turns.enable = true
    Turns.order = {"Blue", "Red", "Green", "Yellow"}
    local tokenBoardRotations = {
        {playerColour = "Red", rotation = Vector(0,45,0)},
        {playerColour = "Green", rotation = Vector(0,135,0)},
        {playerColour = "Yellow", rotation = Vector(0,225,0)},
        {playerColour = "Blue", rotation = Vector(0,315,0)}
    }
    local seatedPlayers = {}
    for _, player in ipairs(Player.getPlayers()) do
        if player.color ~= "Black" then
            if player.color ~= "Grey" then
                table.insert(seatedPlayers, player.color)
            end
        end
    end
    local tokenBoard = nil
    for i, o in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if o.hasTag("Tokenboard") then
            tokenBoard = o
        end
    end
    local randomSelection = math.random(1, #seatedPlayers)
    local tokenBoardRotation = tokenBoard.getRotation()
    for j, p in ipairs(tokenBoardRotations) do
        if p.playerColour == seatedPlayers[randomSelection] then
            local firstPlayerRotation = tokenBoardRotation:add(p.rotation)
            tokenBoard.setRotation(firstPlayerRotation)
        end
    end
    Turns.turn_color = seatedPlayers[randomSelection]
    printToAll("Harmonies: " .. seatedPlayers[randomSelection] .. " was selected to go first")
end

function onChat(message, sender)
    if message == "!spirits" then
        if spirits == false then
            setupSpirits()
            spirits = true
        end
    end
    if message == "!refill" then
        refillAnimals()
    end
end


function setupSpirits()
    local spiritCards = {}
    for i, s in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if s.hasTag("Spirit") then
            s.setLock(false)
            table.insert(spiritCards, s)
            s.setPosition({-36.1, 0.1 + (i / 30), 0})
        end
    end
    local groupedSpirits = group(spiritCards)
    groupedSpirits[1].setPosition({-17, 2.1, 0})
    Wait.frames(function() groupedSpirits[1].flip() end, 15, 1)
    Wait.frames(function() groupedSpirits[1].randomize() end, 30, 1)
    local dealOrder = {
        "Red",
        "Blue",
        "Green",
        "Yellow",
        "Red",
        "Blue",
        "Green",
        "Yellow",
    }
    Wait.time(function() Wait.time(function() spiritsCycle(groupedSpirits[1], dealOrder) end, 0.2, 8) end, 0.75, 1)
end

function spiritsCycle(deck, order)
    spiritIndex = spiritIndex + 1
    --for _, player in ipairs(Player.getPlayers()) do
    --    if player.color == order[spiritIndex] then
    --        deck.deal(1, order[spiritIndex])
    --    end
    --end
    deck.deal(1, order[spiritIndex])
end

function setupAnimals()
    local animalCards = {}
    for i, s in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if s.hasTag("Animal") then
            s.setLock(false)
            table.insert(animalCards, s)
            s.setPosition(Vector(animalDeckPosition.x, animalDeckPosition.y + (i / 30), animalDeckPosition.z))
        end
    end
    local groupedAnimals = group(animalCards)
    groupedAnimals[1].setPosition(animalDeckPosition)
    Wait.frames(function() groupedAnimals[1].flip() end, 15, 1)
    Wait.frames(function() groupedAnimals[1].randomize() end, 30, 1)
    Wait.time(function() Wait.time(function() dealAnimalsCycle(groupedAnimals[1], animalPositions) end, 0.1, 5) end, 0.75, 1)
end

function dealAnimalsCycle(deck, position)
    animalIndex = animalIndex + 1
    local params = {
        position = animalPositions[animalIndex],
        flip = true
    }
    local takenObject = deck.takeObject(params)
end

function setupTokens()
    local tokenBag = nil
    local tokenBoard = nil
    for i, s in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if s.hasTag("Tokenbag") then
            tokenBag = s
        end
        if s.hasTag("Tokenboard") then
            tokenBoard = s
        end
    end
    tokenBag.randomize()
    local tokenSnaps = tokenBoard.getSnapPoints()
    local emptySnaps = {}
    for i, s in ipairs(tokenSnaps) do
        --log(s.position)
        --log("\n")
        --Player["White"].pingTable(tokenBoard.positionToWorld(s.position))
        local snapPos = tokenBoard.positionToWorld(s.position)
        local ray = findObjects(snapPos)
        if ray[1].hit_object.hasTag("Tokenboard") then
            table.insert(emptySnaps, Vector(tokenBoard.positionToWorld(s.position)))
        end
    end
    tokenIndex = 0
    if #emptySnaps > 0 then
        Wait.time(function() refillTokens(tokenBag, emptySnaps) end, 0.1, #emptySnaps)
    end
end

function refillTokens(bag, positions)
    tokenIndex = tokenIndex + 1
    local params = {
        position = Vector(positions[tokenIndex].x, positions[tokenIndex].y + 0.5, positions[tokenIndex].z),
    }
    local takenObject = bag.takeObject(params)
end

function refillAnimals()
    allObjects = getAllObjects()
    local animalDeck = nil
    for i, o in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if o.hasTag("Animal") then
            if o.tag == "Deck" then
                animalDeck = o
            end
        end
    end
    local emptyAnimals = {}
    for i, p in ipairs(animalPositions) do
        if findObjects(p)[1].hit_object.tag ~= "Card" then
            local params = {position = p, flip = true}
            animalDeck.takeObject(params)
        end
    end
end

function refillCubes(object, player, alt)
    local pos = Vector(object.getPosition())
    local posOffset = pos:add(Vector(0,5,0))
    local findCard = findObjects(posOffset)
    local card = nil
    local cardSnaps = nil
    for o, object in ipairs(findCard) do
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("Animal") then
            card = object.hit_object
            cardSnaps = object.hit_object.getSnapPoints()
        end
    end
    local findCubes = findCast(pos,Vector(3.7,1,6.2),3)
    for c, cube in ipairs(findCubes) do
        if cube.hit_object.hasTag("Token") then
            cube.hit_object.destruct()
        end
    end
    for s, snap in ipairs(cardSnaps) do
        local pos = Vector(card.positionToWorld(snap.position)):add(Vector(0,1,0))
        scoreCubeBag.takeObject({position=pos})
    end
end

function findObjects(pos)
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = pos,
        direction    = {0,-1,0},
        type         = 3,
        size         = {0.1,0.1,0.1},
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = false,
    })
    return hitList
end

function findCast(pos,size,type)
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = pos,
        direction    = {0,-1,0},
        type         = type,
        size         = size,
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = false,
    })
    return hitList
end
